Abhee kuch dinon se lagaa raha hai badle-badle se hum hain
Hum baithe-baithe din mein sapane dekhte, neenden kam hain
Abhee kuch dinon se sunaa hai dil ka rob hee kuch naya hai
Koyi raaj kambakht hai chhupaae, khuda hee jaane ki kya hai
Hai dil pe shaq mera, ise pyaar ho gaya

Too be-khabar ya saba khabar

Pardon mein main rakh loon tuje
Ki dil tera aa naa jae kaheen ye gair par
Hum bhole hain, sharmile hain
Hum hain zaraa sidhe, maasoom itanee kair kar
Jis din kabhi zid pe ade
Hum aayenge aag ka tera dariyaa tair kar
Abhee kuch dinon se lage mera dil dhut ho jaise nashe mein
Kyun ladkadaae, ye bahake, gae, hai tere har raaste mein
Hai dil pe shaq mera, ise pyaar ho gaya

Man ke shahar chal raat-bhar
Too aur main do musaafir, bhatakate hum phiren
Chal, raaste jahaan le chalem
Sapanon ke phir dariyaaon mein thak ke hum giren
Koyi pyaar kee tarqeeb ho
Nuskhe koyi jo sikhaye to hum bhee sikh len
Ye pyaar hai rahata kahaan?
Koyi humse kahe, us se jaa ke puch le
Main sanbhaaluun paanv, fisal naa jaaoon, naee-naee dosti hai

Koyi raaj kambakht hai chhupaae, khuda hee jaane ki kya hai
Hai dil pe shaq mera, ise pyaar ho gaya
Abhee kuch dinon se main sochtha hoon  ki dil kee thodee see sun loon
Yahaan rahne aaegee, dil sajaa loon, main khwaab thode se bun loon
Hai dil pe shaq mera, ise pyaar ho gaya

Too be-khabar ya saba khabar
Ik din zaraa mere maasoom dil pe gaur kar
Pardon mein main rakh loon tuje
Ki dil tera aa naa jae kaheen ye gair par
Hum bhole hain, sharmile hain
Hum hain zaraa sidhe, maasoom itanee kair kar
Jis din kabhi zid pe ade
Hum aayenge aag ka tera dariyaa tair kar
Abhee kuch dinon se lage mera dil dhut ho jaise nashe mein
Kyun ladkadaae, ye bahake, gae, hai tere har raaste mein
Hai dil pe shaq mera, ise pyaar ho gaya

Man ke shahar chal raat-bhar
Too aur main do musaafir, bhatakate hum phiren
Chal, raaste jahaan le chalem
Sapanon ke phir dariyaaon mein thak ke hum giren
Koyi pyaar kee tarqeeb ho
Nuskhe koyi jo sikhaye to hum bhee sikh len
Ye pyaar hai rahata kahaan?
Koyi humse kahe, us se jaa ke puch le
Main sanbhaaluun paanv, fisal naa jaaoon, naee-naee dosti hai
zaraa dekh-bhaal
